under his wing and see.

117
00:08:18,353 --> 00:08:19,320
-Well, in that case.

118
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,120
-Thank you all very much.

119
00:08:27,153 --> 00:08:28,087
-Uh-- yeah.

120
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,287
Thank you.

121
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:32,087
-And with that, our mission
is pretty much complete.

122
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:32,620
-No.

123
00:08:32,653 --> 00:08:33,753
Not just yet.

124
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:56,220
NEJI: You all right?

125
00:08:56,253 --> 00:08:58,953
-What does it matter if I'm
feeling all right or not?

126
00:08:58,987 --> 00:09:02,053
