all alone like I am.

127
00:09:02,087 --> 00:09:02,820
-Hey, come on.

128
00:09:02,853 --> 00:09:03,920
Don't say that.

129
00:09:03,953 --> 00:09:05,987
-Why don't we just leave
this weakling here?

130
00:09:06,020 --> 00:09:08,520
