good friends in your life

132
00:09:10,787 --> 00:09:12,387
who you can count on in a pinch?

133
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:14,820
-I'm talking about
the basics here.

134
00:09:14,853 --> 00:09:17,753
I can't stand weak,
indecisive people.

135
00:09:17,787 --> 00:09:21,287
-Since the day I was born,
I've always been frail.

136
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:23,653
And for most of my
life, a shabby cabin

137
00:09:23,687 --> 00:09:25,120
was my entire world.

138
00:09:30,053 --> 00:09:33,587
I have no memory of my parents.

139
00:09:33,620 --> 00:09:37,120
I survived only because the
villagers took pity on me

140
00:09:37,153 --> 00:09:39,687
and brought me small amounts
of food from time to time.

141
00:09:42,620 --> 00:09:46,353
But even as fragile as I
was, I had a special power

142
00:09:46,387 --> 00:09:47,220
no one else did.

143
00:10:10,953 --> 00:10:13,420
-Here you go.

144
00:10:13,453 --> 00:10:15,253
Th-- thanks you.

145
00:10:15,287 --> 00:10:17,387
You cut your leg with a scythe.

146
00:10:17,420 --> 00:10:18,820
Is it better now?

147
00:10:18,853 --> 00:10:19,487
-Wait.

148
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:20,353
How did you know that?

149
00:10:20,387 --> 00:10:21,887
Did I tell you?

150
00:10:21,920 --> 00:10:22,720
-No.

151
00:10:22,753 --> 00:10:24,887
I just knew about it.

152
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:26,687
-But-- but how?

153
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:30,753
I'm the only one who's been
here to see you since yesterday.

154
00:10:30,787 --> 00:10:33,887
I saw it happen to
you from where I sit.

155
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:34,687
-No.

156
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:37,553
He's cursed!

157
00:10:37,587 --> 00:10:42,420
RANMARU: as time went
on, everyone feared me.

158
00:10:42,453 --> 00:10:44,120
I could see what was
happening outside.

159
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:48,887
-Did you hear?

160
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:51,987
That Ranmaru boy can see
everything we're doing.

161
00:10:52,020 --> 00:10:55,020
-You mean to tell me we're
being spied on every day?

162
00:10:55,053 --> 00:10:55,987
-Get out of here!

163
00:10:56,020 --> 00:10:57,953
-We don't want your kind here!

164
00:10:57,987 --> 00:10:58,920
-Get out of my village!

165
00:10:58,953 --> 00:11:01,287
-Monster!

166
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:05,053
RANMARU: From then on, I had no
more visitors bringing me food.

167
00:11:05,087 --> 00:11:08,387
All I could do is wait to die.

168
00:11:08,420 --> 00:11:11,420
If it weren't for Raiga,
I wouldn't be alive.

169
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:19,220
-His past is so tragic.

170
00:11:19,253 --> 00:11:20,820
I had no idea.

171
00:11:20,853 --> 00:11:21,320
-Yes.

172
00:11:21,353 --> 00:11:24,253
I agree.

173
00:11:24,287 --> 00:11:26,120
-Raiga took me out
beyond those walls,

174
00:11:26,153 --> 00:11:29,053
showing me a world I had
never experienced before.

175
00:11:34,987 --> 00:11:37,120
-Ranmaru, open your eyes.

176
00:11:40,187 --> 00:11:42,753
Take a look at the
outside world where

177
00:11:42,787 --> 00:11:46,520
we'll be living
from now on, yes?

178
00:11:46,553 --> 00:11:47,020
-Yes.

179
00:11:50,553 --> 00:11:52,887
If Raiga isn't here
to care for me,

180
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:56,353
it's the same as
losing my own body.

181
00:11:56,387 --> 00:11:58,153
-I think I see.

182
00:11:58,187 --> 00:12:01,887
Raiga was able to become one
of the famous Seven Swordsmen,

183
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:05,153
because he was able to
borrow power from Ranmaru.

184
00:12:05,187 --> 00:12:08,920
-So the two of you helped each
other to survive, didn't you?

185
00:12:08,953 --> 00:12:10,087
-Yeah.

186
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,687
-That's not true!

187
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:15,553
Raiga was using you, so he could
do all those terrible things!

188
00:12:15,587 --> 00:12:16,353
-Yes.

189
00:12:16,387 --> 00:12:17,953
He might have been using me.

190
00:12:17,987 --> 00:12:20,420
It's possible.

191
00:12:20,453 --> 00:12:24,520
But whether good or bad, either
way it doesn't matter to me.

192
00:12:24,553 --> 00:12:27,620
Because I'm just a tool to
sense things out anyway.

193
00:12:27,653 --> 00:12:29,053
-Well, if that's
what you believe,

194
00:12:29,087 --> 00:12:32,720
