to give it your all.

198
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:39,420
And you could start by
eating the curry of life.

199
00:12:39,453 --> 00:12:40,920
That's sure to cheer you up!

200
00:12:40,953 --> 00:12:41,487
-Yes.

201
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,287
That is right.

202
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,253
It will surely nourish you.

203
00:12:44,287 --> 00:12:45,320
-Wait a sec.

204
00:12:45,353 --> 00:12:48,087
