As a matter of fact, the
more I eat of that slop,

208
00:12:55,587 --> 00:12:57,620
the more I feel rejuvenated!

209
00:12:57,653 --> 00:13:00,020
-And it was that very
curry that saved my life.

210
00:13:00,053 --> 00:13:00,853
