be your body for you.

213
00:13:08,820 --> 00:13:11,187
Well?

214
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:11,987
-All right.

215
00:13:12,020 --> 00:13:13,987
But I have one favor to ask.

216
00:13:14,020 --> 00:13:14,487
-Huh?

217
00:13:34,804 --> 00:13:35,271
-Byakugan.

218
00:13:47,871 --> 00:13:48,804
Nothing.

219
00:13:48,837 --> 00:13:50,737
I sense no life in Raiga.

220
00:13:50,771 --> 00:13:54,437
-Can you see down
there, Ranmaru?

221
00:13:54,471 --> 00:13:54,937
-Yes.

222
00:14:00,971 --> 00:14:02,671
-Is everything OK?

223
00:14:02,704 --> 00:14:04,837
-Yeah.

224
00:14:04,871 --> 00:14:05,637
-Let's go.

225
00:14:05,671 --> 00:14:06,471
