237
00:14:40,071 --> 00:14:40,804
-Yeah.

238
00:14:40,837 --> 00:14:42,704
And Karashi is with them.

239
00:14:42,737 --> 00:14:45,937
-Well, that's no reason to
forget your manners, now is it?

240
00:14:45,971 --> 00:14:49,237
-But, Grandma, you mean--
well, aren't you happy?

241
00:14:49,271 --> 00:14:52,971
-One and two, one and two.

242
00:14:53,004 --> 00:14:53,737
-Careful.

243
00:14:53,771 --> 00:14:55,204
