250
00:15:15,704 --> 00:15:18,337
-Please, pardon his
behavior, ma'am.

251
00:15:18,371 --> 00:15:20,571
From now on he is a changed man.

252
00:15:20,604 --> 00:15:22,104
He will devote
himself to taking over

253
00:15:22,137 --> 00:15:24,437
the Curry of Life restaurant
if you will let him.

254
00:15:29,837 --> 00:15:31,137
-First things first.

255
00:15:31,171 --> 00:15:32,237
