262
00:15:40,637 --> 00:15:43,871
-Actually, I've prepared
a plate for everybody.

263
00:15:43,904 --> 00:15:44,971
Well, look at him.

264
00:15:45,004 --> 00:15:45,771
My.

265
00:15:45,804 --> 00:15:47,937
